in country.

25:43.543 --> 25:44.775
I was.

25:45.077 --> 25:46.443
I am.

25:47.013 --> 25:51.949
-How'd you get leave
to come back?
-New policy.

25:53.553 --> 25:56.253
It's a little different
from my day.

25:57.490 --> 25:58.989
Lots of things are.

26:14.006 --> 26:18.475
SAM: <i> Sixty-one unsolved</i>
<i> crimes in your neighborhood</i>
<i> last year.</i>

26:18.477 --> 26:20.377
CARTER: <i> You think</i>
