26:41.734 --> 26:42.766
<i> That's a good one.</i>

26:42.768 --> 26:45.269
I don't know why
you got to make it personal.

26:45.571 --> 26:47.137
You know? Leo.

26:47.139 --> 26:49.273
All right, so...
So you want me

26:49.275 --> 26:50.140
to identify the guy?

26:50.142 --> 26:53.344
-'Cause I told you
that I was at the studio...
-Leo, Leo, Leo, Leo.

26:53.346 --> 26:54.878
You know why you're here.

26:54.880 --> 26:57.281
On some level, you got to be
a little relieved, right?

26:57.283 --> 27:00.284
All right, all right.
You know what? I knew it.

27:00.286 --> 27:02.686
Here's the thing
about murder, Leo.

27:02.688 --> 27:06.624
You deny it, get arrested,
get charged, found guilty,

27:06.626 --> 27:09.460
make us spend all that time
and money, you fry.

27:09.462 --> 27:10.527
When you and I both know that

27:10.529 --> 27:14.098
you'll barely make it
past the charge part.

27:14.233 --> 27:15.499
Doctors gave you what?

27:15.501 --> 27:17.935
Six months? Six months?

27:17.937 --> 27:21.171
No DA wants to walk you
into a courtroom.

27:23.776 --> 27:24.642
I called my lawyer.

27:24.644 --> 27:27.711
-And he's gonna be here.
He's gonna be here anytime.
-Okay.

27:27.713 --> 27:29.747
He was my wife's lawyer
back in the day, yeah.

27:29.749 --> 27:31.148
Oh, wow. I know him?

27:31.150 --> 27:33.083
(LAUGHS) Robert Rollins.

27:33.085 --> 27:34.618
-Oh, he's a big gun, yeah.
-That's right.

27:34.620 --> 27:38.389
And he loved Joycie, so I'm
not saying anything. Nothing.

27:38.391 --> 27:39.823
Charmain? Can I talk to you
for a minute?

27:39.825 --> 27:40.758
I'm saying nothing, nothing.

27:40.760 --> 27:43.027
That's good, Leo.
You did a good thing.

27:43.029 --> 27:45.062
-A very, very good thing.
-Mmm-hmm.

27:45.064 --> 27:46.964
You just sit tight
right there,

27:46.966 --> 27:51.435
and, uh, I'm gonna walk
and talk to your neighbor
Mrs. Lee

27:51.437 --> 27:54.571
and get a sworn statement
from her that you were home.

27:54.573 --> 27:56.940
Then I'm gonna talk
to that young man over there,

27:56.942 --> 27:59.910
who says he heard your wife
scream shortly
before 8:00 a.m.

27:59.912 --> 28:01.945
-Oh.
-Yeah, he was right
outside your door

28:01.947 --> 28:03.614
passing out those leaflets.

28:03.616 --> 28:04.715
No, no, no.

28:04.717 --> 28:06.950
-You arrested him, all right?
-Bye-bye, alibi, Leo.

28:06.952 --> 28:08.118
He's not helping you.
He's not helping you.

28:08.120 --> 28:10.020
