a little convincing.

28:11.390 --> 28:12.856
-(DOOR OPENS)
-Charmain.

28:12.858 --> 28:16.527
The lawyer for
a Mr. Leo Nankin
is gonna be coming.

28:16.529 --> 28:17.761
-Robert Rollins.
-Rollins, Rollins.

28:17.763 --> 28:22.099
Yeah, I want you to make sure
that he gets here right away.

28:22.301 --> 28:23.701
Thank you.

28:24.670 --> 28:25.869
Okay, Leo.

28:25.871 --> 28:31.508
What I finally got
is an actual case,
which I do not want.

28:31.510 --> 28:35.446
But I also don't want another
open homicide on my desk.

28:35.581 --> 28:38.348
I will give you
my word of honor that you

28:38.350 --> 28:40.584
will never see the inside
of a jail or a court.

28:40.586 --> 28:42.753
-Can I talk to you?
-No.

28:42.922 --> 28:44.288
-Outside.
-No.

28:44.290 --> 28:45.222
Outside, just a second.

28:45.224 --> 28:47.691
Leo, you know
how much you hate
the coloreds?

28:47.693 --> 28:51.295
-I need to talk to you.
-Well, not half as much
as they hate you.

28:51.297 --> 28:53.197
And they can burn you today.

28:53.199 --> 28:54.698
Hodiak, I need to talk to you.

28:54.700 --> 28:56.100
But you confess,
and you get to go home.

28:56.102 --> 28:59.369
No, I need to talk to you
right now, outside.

28:59.371 --> 29:00.738
Thank you.

29:01.273 --> 29:02.506
Look...

29:03.676 --> 29:05.008
(KNOCKING)
Are you serious?

29:05.010 --> 29:07.311
(JIGGLES DOORKNOB)
Open the door, Hodiak.

29:07.546 --> 29:08.912
(BANGING)

29:09.381 --> 29:10.347
Hodiak!

29:10.349 --> 29:12.015
-Open...
-Charmain.

29:12.017 --> 29:13.350
Let's go. Women's booking.

29:13.352 --> 29:15.519
-No, I...
-Come on.

29:16.188 --> 29:16.687
Hey.

29:16.689 --> 29:18.188
-You know what's up, right?
-Huh?

29:18.190 --> 29:19.189
