of the building.

29:23.763 --> 29:25.829
-In booking, you say.
-Hey! (CLAPPING)

29:25.831 --> 29:27.331
Come on, let's go.

29:27.333 --> 29:28.866
-Okay.
-You know what? Yeah, I...

29:28.868 --> 29:30.400
-You got it?
-I'd be happy to, yes.

29:30.402 --> 29:32.703
My lawyer's gonna be
here in just a moment, second.

29:32.705 --> 29:34.738
As soon as he does,
you're gonna spend the rest

29:34.740 --> 29:38.041
of what's left of your life
in jail.

29:38.410 --> 29:40.110
You want that?

29:41.147 --> 29:42.446
