30:11.477 --> 30:12.409
(SOBBING) Yeah.

30:12.411 --> 30:16.680
Yeah, she knew this was
an important birthday.

30:19.852 --> 30:22.152
That's the thing
about wives, Leo.

30:22.154 --> 30:23.387
They're never
the worst thing they say

30:23.389 --> 30:27.024
or the best thing they do,
and neither are we.

30:30.262 --> 30:32.296
Okay, all right.

30:35.467 --> 30:37.301
Okay, come on, Leo.

30:37.469 --> 30:39.736
