31:18.377 --> 31:20.777
-Did you sign?
-Yes.

31:23.015 --> 31:24.414
Thank you.

31:24.416 --> 31:25.849
You're under arrest.

31:25.851 --> 31:27.150
Hands behind your back.

31:27.152 --> 31:28.218
