you have the right
to remain silent.

31:51.844 --> 31:53.110
(SIGHS)

31:54.346 --> 31:57.247
-Oh. Indian giver.
-Yeah.

31:58.050 --> 31:59.283
(SIGHS)

31:59.618 --> 32:04.187
